ZH: 你可以询问他的名字吗？
EN: Can you ask him his name?

ZH: 请问这里有没有公共厕所？
EN: Excuse me, is there a public toilet here?

ZH: 我想询问一下您的手机号码。
EN: I would like to ask for your phone number.

ZH: 他不愿意回答我的问题，所以我只好询问别人。
EN: He didn't want to answer my questions, so I had to ask someone else.

ZH: 他来到我面前询问我是否需要帮助。
EN: He approached me and asked if I needed any help.

ZH: 如果您有任何疑问，请随时询问。
EN: If you have any questions, feel free to ask.

ZH: 我打算去询问一下工作面试的结果。
EN: I'm planning to go and inquire about the results of my job interview.

ZH: 我向老师询问如何做出这个实验。
EN: I asked the teacher how to conduct this experiment.

ZH: 我们应该向专业人士询问这个问题。
EN: We should ask a professional about this issue.

ZH: 他来到我们办公室询问如何预约一位医生。
EN: He came to our office to inquire about how to schedule an appointment with a doctor.

ZH: 我想要询问这条路的方向。
EN: I want to ask for directions to this street.

ZH: 他走过来询问我们是否需要帮助。
EN: He came over and asked if we needed any help.

ZH: 我们可以向导游询问当地的旅游景点。
EN: We can ask the tour guide about the local tourist attractions.

ZH: 他向警察询问丢失物品的报案程序。
EN: He inquired with the police about the procedure for reporting lost items.

ZH: 我们应该去银行询问利率和贷款条件。
EN: We should go to the bank to inquire about interest rates and loan conditions.

ZH: 我向老板询问是否可以请假一天。
EN: I asked the boss if I could take a day off.

ZH: 请问你们的营业时间是多久？
EN: Excuse me, how long is your business hours?

ZH: 我打算给公司总经理写封邮件询问关于这个计划的详情。
EN: I plan to send an email to the company's CEO to inquire about the details of this plan.

ZH: 你可以去受理处询问关于这个事情的进展。
EN: You can go to the reception desk to ask about the progress of this matter.

ZH: 我向邻居询问是否有人看到我的猫。
EN: I asked my neighbor if anyone had seen my cat.
